{"TopicId":211530,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Possible Spyware on games from Steam using Steamworks.net","CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T15:47:38Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T15:47:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGuys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust came to my attention that Steams users, apparently, are susceptible to an attack to their privacy by Steam\u0027s games using \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.net\u003C/span\u003E .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs it appears, \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#f39c12;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.net\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E is sending information to\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Esurvey-smiles.com\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E , currently under the IP\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E199.59.243.222\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E .\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t confirm this yet because, besides had bought KSP on Steam, I download my games using \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003Edownload_depot\u003C/span\u003E on the Steam Client\u0027s Console and install them manually.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the mean time, the best defense is to block the offending site (or its IP) on your firewall. \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.net\u003C/span\u003E is open source, so it\u0027s possible to recompile it ripping of the offending code - but Steam will happily overwrite your changes as soon as you update the game or verify the installation - but if you are like me and install everything by hand, an alternative \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.net\u003C/span\u003E binary without spyware could be a nice side project to someone with some time to burn!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u2014 EDIT \u2014\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIt came to my attention that, perhaps, \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.net\u003C/span\u003E could be being compromised on the user\u0027s machine, perhaps by virii, perhaps by code injection!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u2014 \u2014 \u2014 \u2014\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-01-16T22:46:25Z\u0022 title=\u002201/16/2023 10:46  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 16, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEDIT\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mahnarch","CreatedById":114432,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T16:06:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI manually install my games with some good ol\u0027 fashioned duct tape and staples.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the heads up, though!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T18:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood thing I don\u0027t use Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll say it again: never trust big companies like that. Never trust Microsoft, Apple, Google, Meta, all that sort of things. They would do anything for money -- including spying of course.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T22:02:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224220301\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211530\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673884058\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022187168\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lisias\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Lisias said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncan\u0027t confirm this yet\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did you get the information from?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-16T22:47:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224220488\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211530\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673906562\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n50 minutes ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did you get the information from?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.google.com/search?q=%22survey-smiles.com%22\u002Bsteam\u0026amp;newwindow=1\u0026amp;client=safari\u0026amp;rls=en\u0026amp;sxsrf=AJOqlzVm3R_HYXOvufHdyoyiyJPSL9iF4w%3A1673908181991\u0026amp;ei=1c_FY4iTPMH31sQPuoiLwAo\u0026amp;ved=0ahUKEwjI0cv0kc38AhXBu5UCHTrEAqgQ4dUDCA4\u0026amp;uact=5\u0026amp;oq=%22survey-smiles.com%22\u002Bsteam\u0026amp;gs_lcp=Cgxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAQAzIFCCEQoAEyBQghEKABMgUIIRCgATIFCCEQoAE6DAgAEAcQHhDxBBCwAzoICAAQgAQQsAM6BQgAEIAEOgcIABAeEPEEOgcIIRCgARAKOggIIRAWEB4QHUoECEEYAUoECEYYAFDOBVjRC2CODWgBcAB4AIABkwGIAfYFkgEDMC42mAEAoAEByAEKwAEB\u0026amp;sclient=gws-wiz-serp\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESteam Forums\u003C/a\u003E. Many players from many games are complaining about this in the last weeks, and I found \u003Ca href=\u0022https://steamcommunity.com/app/504050/discussions/0/3766731192692461115/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethis post\u003C/a\u003E about a guy saying it zeroed it on the \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.NET\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know if this stunt is being pulled by someone at Steam, or if 3rd parties managed to inject malicious code on the \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.NET\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0on the user\u0027s machine (virii?) to do that - and I don\u0027t even know if this affects only Windows users or also Linux and MacOS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI decided to post this here because \u003Ca href=\u0022https://steamworks.github.io/gameslist/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKSP is listed as one of the games\u003C/a\u003E using \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003ESteamworks.NET\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0and people here is usually\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eway\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0savvier on this field than the community of most games I\u0027m aware - so the chances of getting this settled/confirmed/whatever here is IMHO way higher than on Steam Forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did a quick search on the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/rlabrecque/Steamworks.NET\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Egithub repo\u003C/a\u003E for \u0022survey\u0022 and \u0022survey-smiles\u0022 but, obviously, didn\u0027t found anything. At least, yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-01-16T22:54:24Z\u0022 title=\u002201/16/2023 10:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 16, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EClicked \u0026quot;Save\u0026quot; too soon.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T02:13:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood thing I pull ksp out of my steam directory\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}